BodyName: Manhattan Delegation of the New York City Council

Items.Title: Pursuant to Section 2403 of the New York City Charter, the members of the Council representing the Borough of Manhattan will meet to vote on the nominations of Mark Brennan-Ing and Mark Meridy for appointment to the Department for the Aging Advisory Council.
Items.MatterName: Members of the Council representing the Borough of Manhattan will meet to vote on the nominations of Mark Brennan-Ing and Mark Meridy for appointment to the Department for the Aging Advisory Council.
